        "subject": "LU-10066 osp: error overflow handling for llog id",
        "message": "LU-10066 osp: error overflow handling for llog id\n\nIn osp_sync_correct_id(), it should be a normal case for the lrh_id\nto be greater than committed_id but it was recognized as overflow,\nthis will cause correct_id to become a negative number.\n\nThis patch makes it correct.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I906ceb8e8aad52cb516a25bda9aae9e8065f6cde\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
